Chile, China, Cuba, Djibouti, Ecuador, France, Gabon, Ghana, Guatemala, 
Japan, Jordan, Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia, Maldives, Mauritania, Mauritius, 
Mexico, Nigeria, Norway, Pakistan, Qatar, Russian Federation, Saudi Arabia, 
Senegal, Spain, Switzerland, Thailand, Uganda, United Kingdom of Great 
Britain and Northern Ireland, Uruguay  
</p>
<p><i> Against: 
</i>United States of America 
</p>
<p><i> Abstaining: 
</i>Cameroon, Hungary, Poland, Republic of Korea, Republic of Moldova, 
Slovakia, Ukraine, Zambia] 
