</p>
<p>833. At the same meeting, statements in exercise of the right of reply were made by the 
representatives of Colombia, Cyprus, Greece and Turkey. 
</p>
<p>834. At the same meeting, a statement in exercise of a second right of reply was made by 
the representative of Turkey. 
