</p>
<p>849. Also at the same meeting, the draft resolution, as orally revised, was adopted 
without a vote (for the text as adopted, see part one, chapter I, resolution 16/35). 
</p><p>850. At the same meeting, the representative of Switzerland (also on behalf of Norway) 
made a statement in explanation of vote after the vote. 
</p>
